{
  "id": "adv_main_03_11_04",
  "title": "BIG4編1章54話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "mihoさん、えっと……収録お疲れ様です\nその……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Miho-san‚ um…good work on the recording.\nUm…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "勝手に収録現場まで押しかけて来るなんて\nマネージャーは貴方達にどんな教育をしているのかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To barge into the recording studio like this…\n…what kind of education is your manager giving you all?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.1431373556
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "こんな状況下で、貴方を一人で寄越すのも考えられない\nマスコミに囲まれたらどうするつもりだったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can’t believe he would send you out here alone\nin this situation. What were you going to do if you were surrounded by the media?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.4219956358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.2881374001
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "収録現場までは、{user}さんが送って\nくれました。それに一人で来たのは私の意志です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Manager-san drove me to the recording studio.\nAnd it was my will to come alone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.11011012
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "……呆れるわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…How absurd.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.11011012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.2266309698
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい。でも、私が本気だと理解してもらうには\nこれが一番だと思ったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry. But I thought this was the best way\nto show you that I'm serious.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.1667438785
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "どりきゅんの過去を知りたいそうだけど\n他人の過去を語る趣味はないし、答える義理もないわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I hear you want to know about DoriKyun’s past‚ but…\n…I have no interest in talking about other people’s pasts‚ nor am I obligated to answer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.9400902708,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "そもそも、なぜそんなことが知りたいの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the first place‚ why do you want to know that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.2992860436,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.9292443554
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "……私は一時期\nれもんさんと来夢さんと行動を共にしていました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…For a while‚\n…I worked with Lemon-san and Laim-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 57.2000000018
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.9521469076
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "そこで、二人の強さや確固たる意志を\n目にしてきたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I saw firsthand\ntheir strength and unwavering will.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.873053817
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "私は、どりきゅんがどうしてあんな風に迷いなく\n進むようになったのか、その理由が、過程が知りたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to know why‚ how‚ DoriKyun\ncame to be able to move forward without hesitation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.1620108724
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "そして、その上で――\nあの二人ともう一度戦いたいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then――\n…I want to fight those two again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.0282903631
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "本気で勝てると思っているの？\n二度も負けて恥を晒しておきながら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do you really think you can win?\nAfter being defeated twice and humiliated‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.8311539292,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "大体、グループを脱退したと思えば敵の下で\n修行を積んで、その上でまた戻ってくるなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "you leave the group‚ train under your enemy‚\nand then come back on top of that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.3311539292,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.3907695094
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "自分がどれほどの恥を晒しているのか\n自覚がないのかしら。図々しいにも程がある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do you have any idea how much you’re embarrassing\nyourself? There’s a limit to how shameless you can be.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.0978205959,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.4845406492
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "mihoさんの言う通りです。私は、私のこれまでの\n行動を正当化するつもりはありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re right‚ Miho-san. I have no\nintention of justifying my actions up until now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.4333318074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.4767417232
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "でも……みっともなくても、恥を晒しても……\n掴みたいものがあるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But…even if it’s unsightly‚ even if I embarrass myself…\n…there’s something I want to grab hold of.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.7999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "周りにどう言われようと、この意志は変わりません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No matter what people around me say‚ this will won’t change.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.1053357719,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.6451769311
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_contact-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 130.4724701206
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.4724701206
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "恥を晒しても……ね……\n………………いいわ。教えてあげる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Embarrass yourself…huh…\n……………Fine. I’ll tell you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.4724701206,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "え？　……あ……ありがとうございます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? …Ah…thank you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.7184477447,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.7184477447
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "あくまで今回だけよ。こんな話をしても\nスリクスにはなんのメリットもないのだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is just this once‚ you hear? There’s no merit\nfor IIIX in talking about this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.0810413003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.0082624554
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "……正直、私も彼女達のことを\n詳しく知っている訳じゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…To be honest‚ I don’t\nreally know much about them either.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.347707967,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_11_04-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、ここ数年のアイドルシーンを引っ張ってきた存在\nだもの、嫌でもいろいろな噂は耳にしたことがあるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But they’ve been leading figures in the idol scene these last few years‚\nso I’ve heard various rumors whether I want to or not.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.247707967,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 161.0295538862
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
