      "text": "当時から周囲とはトラブルを起こしていたらしいわ\n生放送中のケンカや騒ぎも一度や二度じゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems they were causing trouble with those around them even back then.\nThey fought and caused a scene during live broadcasts more than once or twice.",
        "id": ""
